    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You are seriously going to love this ride. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
