    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a pinnacle of the analog driving era. The S54 power plant features a meticulously maintained valvetrain with recent valve clearance adjustments and a fully addressed double-VANOS system. The chassis rigidity is uncompromised, benefiting from a proactive subframe reinforcement and a precision-aligned suspension utilizing OEM+ Bilstein dampers. The ZF 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. This vehicle exhibits zero fluid seepage, no bushing deflection, and a pristine undercarriage, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
