    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom-quality specimen, meticulously maintained to satisfy the most demanding collector. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating and a life spent exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. The wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in a recently installed set of premium performance tires. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it has never been smoked in. Every electronic feature and driver assist functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history exclusively from authorized dealerships. All fluids were recently flushed, and the vehicle has passed a rigorous multi-point inspection with flying colors. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
